                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='14434' id='6' type-v2='text' w='99002' x='499' y='924'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontsize='20'>Income Classification - Model Interpretation</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>Feature importance analysis identifies which variables most influence the prediction of high income (&gt;50K). </run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>Gradient Boosted Trees and Random Forest provide insight into the relative contribution of demographic and employment features.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
