              </zone>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone h='28522' id='14' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='99002' x='499' y='70554'>
            <zone forceUpdate='true' h='25751' id='15' type-v2='text' w='99002' x='499' y='70554'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>Key Insights</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>1. Occupation (</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>OCCP</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>), Education Level (</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>SCHL</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>), and Age (</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>AGEP</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>) are the most influential predictors of income classification across both models.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>2. Additional variables including Working Hours (</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>WKHP</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>), Sex (</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>SEX</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>), and Marital Status (</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>MAR</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>) also contribute to the prediction, indicating that both labour market characteristics and demographic factors influence income levels.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>3. The consistency between Gradient Boosted Trees and Random Forest suggests that these predictors are robust determinants of high income (&gt;50K).</run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
